lead_paragraph: Dean Elgar has been called up by South Africa to replace injured batsman Rilee Rossouw for the rest of the Tri-Nation One-Day International series in the West Indies, Cricket South Africa said on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: South Africa Call Up Elgar to Replace Injured Rossouw in ODI Series
